     F** AB#R62 *******************************
     F*  ..ACCOUNTS RECEIVABLE DETAIL LIST..  *
     F*    I-HASADA               97.08.12    *
     F*    GBC             99.09.06 (9999-FOR ALL USERS)
     F*
